						               													<description>Spoing is a capture game that can be played with a Series: Shibumi set , as it uses a 4x4 holes board and balls in three colours (white, black and red).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Setup:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Place 8 black balls and 8 white balls according to this figure. Red balls are considered &amp;lsquo;neutral&amp;rsquo;:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two players, White and Black, alternate turns moving a ball of their colour or a neutral ball (red) to jump over a single ball of another colour and land on any ball to capture it. Jumps may be diagonal (as per Checkers) or orthogonal. Players must capture a ball each turn.&amp;#10;The ball landed on is removed and the ball jumped over is converted to the colour that is not the jumper or the jumpee, e.g. if the jumper is a white ball and the jumpee is a black ball then the jumpee gets replaced with a neutral ball (red).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends immediately when a player can't move on their turn (which could happen if there are not three balls in a row somewhere, or if all remaining triples are unusable by the player). The winner is the player with the most balls of their colour on the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Included in the Shibumi Rule Book&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Soft cover:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;http://www.lulu.com/shop/cameron-browne-and-nestor-romeral-andres/shibumi-rule-book/paperback/product-18940123.html&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Downloadable PDF:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;http://www.nestorgames.com/rulebooks/SHIBUMI_EN.pdf&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
